BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 206.64 740 Td (CHAPTER 1: WHAT IS CBT?) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 700 Td (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy \(CBT\) is an evidence-based psychological) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 682 Td (treatment that has been proven effective for anxiety disorders.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 646 Td (The core principle of CBT is that our THOUGHTS affect our FEELINGS,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (which in turn affect our BEHAVIORS. By changing unhelpful thought) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 610 Td (patterns, we can reduce anxiety and improve our quality of life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 592 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 574 Td (THE CBT TRIANGLE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 556 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 538 Td (  THOUGHTS \(what we think\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 520 Td (       |) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 502 Td (  FEELINGS \(what we feel emotionally and physically\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 484 Td (       |) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 466 Td (  BEHAVIORS \(what we do or avoid\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 448 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 430 Td (HOW THIS WORKBOOK WORKS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 412 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 394 Td (1. You will learn to IDENTIFY your anxious thoughts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 376 Td (2. You will EXAMINE the evidence for and against these thoughts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 358 Td (3. You will CHALLENGE cognitive distortions) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 340 Td (4. You will CREATE balanced, realistic alternatives) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 322 Td (5. You will EXPERIMENT with new behaviors) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 304 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 286 Td (CBT is not about positive thinking - it is about REALISTIC thinking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 268 Td (You will learn to evaluate your thoughts like a scientist,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 250 Td (testing hypotheses rather than accepting anxious predictions as facts.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
