q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (Find a comfortable position. Close your eyes. Take three deep breaths.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td (FEET: Curl your toes tightly. Hold 5 seconds. Release. Notice the difference.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td (CALVES: Point your toes up toward your shins. Hold 5 sec. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (THIGHS: Squeeze your thigh muscles. Hold 5 seconds. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td (STOMACH: Tighten your abdominal muscles. Hold 5 seconds. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (CHEST: Take a deep breath and hold it. Hold 5 seconds. Exhale slowly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td (HANDS: Make tight fists. Hold 5 seconds. Release. Spread fingers wide.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td (ARMS: Flex your biceps. Hold 5 seconds. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (SHOULDERS: Shrug shoulders to your ears. Hold 5 seconds. Drop them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td (NECK: Gently press head back. Hold 5 seconds. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td (FACE: Scrunch your entire face. Hold 5 seconds. Release.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (Now scan your body from feet to head. Notice any remaining tension.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td (Breathe into those areas. Allow your whole body to feel heavy and warm.) Tj ET
