q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 700 Td (THE 4-7-8 TECHNIQUE \(Dr. Andrew Weil\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 680 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 663 Td (1. Exhale completely through your mouth, making a whoosh sound.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 646 Td (2. Close your mouth and inhale quietly through your nose for 4 counts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 629 Td (3. Hold your breath for 7 counts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 612 Td (4. Exhale completely through your mouth for 8 counts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 595 Td (5. This is one breath cycle. Repeat 3 more times \(4 cycles total\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 578 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 561 Td (Practice twice daily. It becomes more effective with repetition.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 544 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 527 Td (BOX BREATHING \(Navy SEAL Technique\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 507 Td (1. Breathe IN for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 490 Td (2. HOLD for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 473 Td (3. Breathe OUT for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 456 Td (4. HOLD for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 439 Td (Repeat 4-6 cycles.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 402 Td (DIAPHRAGMATIC BREATHING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 382 Td (1. Place one hand on chest, one on belly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 365 Td (2. Breathe in slowly - only belly hand should rise.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 348 Td (3. Exhale slowly - belly falls. Chest stays still.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 90 331 Td (4. Practice 5-10 minutes daily.) Tj ET

endstream
